Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.36,0:35:44.12,中文,,0,0,0,,火草种子现在对鹦鹉来说更容易了\N{\rEng}The seeds of fire grass are now easier for the p
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.12,0:35:47.56,中文,,0,0,0,,在漆黑的大地上寻找……\N{\rEng}to find on the blackened earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.56,0:35:50.72,中文,,0,0,0,,..它们是鹦鹉最喜欢的食物。\N{\rEng}..and they are the parrots' favourite food.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.00,0:36:03.76,中文,,0,0,0,,所以，对于成年人和刚孵出的雏鸟来说......\N{\rEng}So, for both adults and their fledgling chicks..
