Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.68,0:36:18.68,中文,,0,0,0,,但他们的草原家园正在缩小，\N{\rEng}But their grassland home is shrinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.68,0:36:23.36,中文,,0,0,0,,这些可爱的鹦鹉中只剩下大约 1,000 只幸存。\N{\rEng}and only about 1,000 of these lovely parrots sti
